{"tid":138870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Factwire營運資金只剩下2球, 僅夠營運半年","createTime":"2017-03-01T03:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T03:11:32.000Z","uid":48083,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f016ed5e0a2ae75cf1e64de6787a9100fb605f16","tid":138870,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"FactWire News Agency 傳真社<br />\n11 mins &middot; <br />\n<br />\n各位香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n衷心感謝你們一直對傳真社的支持。<br />\n<br />\n今天三月一日是傳真社正式運作一周年，我們至今共發表20多篇具影響力的調查報道，揭發的事件涉及:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">- 核電站安全<br />\n- 港鐵新購列車安全<br />\n- 立法會選舉投票程序<br />\n- 退休高官富商霸佔官地<br />\n- 大廈維修圍標<br />\n- 新航管系統....</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n...等關乎重大公眾利益的新聞。<br />\n<br />\n這是我們過去一年運作的收支簡報。 沒有你們的支持，這家當初由3,300名香港市民集資創辦的新聞機構不可能走到今天。<br />\n<br />\n[url]目前我們的現金只夠運作半年左右，請繼續支持我們的眾籌計劃。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus%5B%2Furl%5D&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c4361afb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17021879_687697868103937_2177126363433323337_n.png?oh=d9b9638b25f648bc592302719ca8e0cf&amp;oe=59722736\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17021879_687697868103937_2177126363433323337_n.png%3Foh%3Dd9b9638b25f648bc592302719ca8e0cf%26oe%3D59722736&h=e271dbec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4266e80cac53fa96a2d56b5d33f37801503d0588","tid":138870,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:15:45.000Z","msg":"香港得返呢間有野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5669137164bfb6894296a0b0c890e206e3d2f964","tid":138870,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"得，放工即捐錢<img src=\"